这一精确到小数点后10,000位的圆周率被别人用烫金数字印刷出来，捐赠给了[[史密森尼学会|史密森尼学会]]<ref>{{cite journal |last=Polachek |first=Harry |coauthors=James Tomayko (ed.) |year=1996 |title=Anecdotes: Computers vs. the Human Race |url=http://www.priorartdatabase.com/IPCOM/000129969/ |accessdate=2009-04-22 |journal=IEEE Annals of the History of Computing |volume=18 |issue=4 |page=60 |publisher=Institute of Electrical and Electronic Engineers |issn=1058-6180 |quote=In order to assure the preservation of this document, I arranged for two clear copies of the output to be printed and specially bound (inscribed in gold letters)—one of which I donated to the Smithsonian Institution in Washington, D.C.; the other I kept. The transfer to the Smithsonian took place at a small ceremony, attended by about 25 invited guests. |doi=10.1109/mahc.1996.539917 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100217000109/http://priorartdatabase.com/IPCOM/000129969/ |archive-date=2010-02-17 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

伦奇还计算了其他一些[[数学常数|数学常数]]，比如将[[欧拉-马歇罗尼常数|欧拉-马歇罗尼常数]] γ计算到小数点后328位<ref>
{{cite journal |last=Wrench, Jr. |first=J. W. |year=1952 |title=A new calculation of Euler's constant |journal=Mathematical Tables and Other Aids to Computation |volume=6 |pages=255 }}
</ref>，将[[辛钦常数|辛钦常数]]计算到小数点后65位<ref>
{{cite journal |last=Shanks |first=Daniel |authorlink=Daniel Shanks |coauthors=J. W. Wrench, Jr. |date=April 1959 |title=Khintchine's Constant |journal=American Mathematical Monthly |volume=66 |issue=5 |pages=276–279 |doi=10.2307/2309633 |publisher=Mathematical Association of America |jstor=2309633 }}
</ref>。

伦奇曾担任《计算数学学报》（''Journal of Mathematics of Computation''）编辑。伦奇是[[美国国家科学院|美国国家科学院]]院士和[[美国国家科学研究委员会|美国国家科学研究委员会]]委员。伦奇共发表约150余篇学术论文。 

